                                        <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
<br />
2017.11.20&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上海" target="_blank">上海</a>-游骑兵&nbsp;阅读&nbsp;189<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8177054/278944048.html" data-pid="278944048">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/01/B0/wKgBEFpMc4mAUY6ZAAEX_Yxz8VY32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278944048" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">2017年11月20号，阴雨。<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/175478.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="始兴县" target="_blank">始兴县</a>。<br />
由于避雨，我们昨天在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/140679.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="大余" target="_blank">大余</a>多停留了一天，上午保养车子，下午休息。因未骑未游，故随记也暂停了一天。<br />
<br />
今天上午七时许，尽管天空还是漂着些许雨丝，我们还是出发了，目标是翻越赣粤边界的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/185213.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="梅岭" target="_blank">梅岭</a>（关），到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10779.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="韶关" target="_blank">韶关</a>市下属<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/175478.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="始兴县" target="_blank">始兴县</a>。<br />
<br />
沿着渐渐上升的坡道，冒着慢慢变大的冷雨，先骑行约9公里，到位于赣粤边界处的梅关风景区去看了一下。<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/185213.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="梅岭" target="_blank">梅岭</a>位于赣粤交界处，地势险要，是长江水系和珠江水系的分水线，而梅关是穿越<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/185213.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="梅岭" target="_blank">梅岭</a>，连接赣粤的交通要道，自古乃兵家必争之地，历史上陈毅就曾在此坚持游击战数年，著有“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/185213.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="梅岭" target="_blank">梅岭</a>三章”等诗作。可今天我骑行到梅关景区门口看了一下，景区入口“有门楼无门人”，考虑到当时正下着中雨，景区入口“人踪皆无”，且进入景区后还要翻山越岭，故选择了放弃游玩，手机拍了几张照片就离开了。<br />
<br />
重回G323国道，再冒雨奋力爬坡约10公里后，我们终于到了梅关隘口---赣粤公路交界处。在这里我们离开了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15508.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江西" target="_blank">江西</a>省，进入了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14674.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广东" target="_blank">广东</a>省，在这里我们还翻越了这次骑行以来的最高海拔365米。很值得纪念一下。为此特诌小诗一首如下：<br />
泥泞走<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63610.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江口" target="_blank">江口</a>，<br />
风雨越<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/185213.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="梅岭" target="_blank">梅岭</a>，<br />
游骑三千里，<br />
今日到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/112697.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="始兴" target="_blank">始兴</a>。<br />
<br />
约上午8.50翻过了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/185213.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="梅岭" target="_blank">梅岭</a>，G323国道就开始了以下坡为主的波浪路，很快车道也由二车道变成了4+2车道且路况也变得更平整些了，此时雨也渐渐变小直至时断时续了，我们的骑行也越来越顺畅，在半途吃了午饭并休息后，下午2.20左右我们完成了82公里的全天骑行，到达了今天的预定目的地<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/175478.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="始兴县" target="_blank">始兴县</a>城并顺利入住。<br />
<br />
到今天为止，我们已经骑游了19天，穿过了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14575.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="浙江" target="_blank">浙江</a>，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15508.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江西" target="_blank">江西</a>两省，累计骑行了约1560公里，总体情况尚好！明天我们计划骑行约40公里到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64130.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="仁化" target="_blank">仁化</a>县入住，游览比较著名的“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10779.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="韶关" target="_blank">韶关</a>丹霞山景区”。后天即骑行约45公里到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10779.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="韶关" target="_blank">韶关</a>，与<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上海" target="_blank">上海</a>坐火车来的队友汇合，开始我们的第三阶段骑游---<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10779.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="韶关" target="_blank">韶关</a>--<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63599.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="徐闻" target="_blank">徐闻</a>。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8177054/278944049.html" data-pid="278944049">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/01/B3/wKgBEFpMc4qAV9j1AAEUW9CZILo98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278944049" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">约上午8,点，来到梅关景区的大门口，。这里属典型的“三无”&nbsp;：无标识，无游客，无工作人员。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8177054/278944050.html" data-pid="278944050">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/01/B4/wKgBEFpMc4uAY7DtAAEOYbcdryA30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278944050" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">远眺雨景中的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/185213.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="梅岭" target="_blank">梅岭</a>。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8177054/278944051.html" data-pid="278944051">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/01/B5/wKgBEFpMc4yADtEDAADk0Jpy3WQ70.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278944051" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">G323国道239公里处，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15508.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江西" target="_blank">江西</a>和<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14674.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广东" target="_blank">广东</a>二省公路交界处。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8177054/278944052.html" data-pid="278944052">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/01/B6/wKgBEFpMc4yAKZqAAAEgrOIC5l841.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278944052" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">离开<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15508.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江西" target="_blank">江西</a>省界了<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8177054/278944053.html" data-pid="278944053">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/01/B6/wKgBEFpMc42AWvp9AAD7bkaKjlM16.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278944053" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/185213.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="梅岭" target="_blank">梅岭</a>隘口山道，坡陡路窄弯急，雨天车多，乃一道险关<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8177054/278944054.html" data-pid="278944054">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/01/B8/wKgBEFpMc46AJgMZAAEqtTuyXhQ15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278944054" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">进入<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14674.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广东" target="_blank">广东</a>，G323国道很快变成了4+2车道，水泥路面也相当平整。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8177054/278944055.html" data-pid="278944055">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/01/B9/wKgBEFpMc46ATmezAADXDGVzEDE27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278944055" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">结束<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/15508.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江西" target="_blank">江西</a>段骑行，进入<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14674.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广东" target="_blank">广东</a>时的欢呼<br />
</p>
    
                        
